description: Welcome to Funnels! The first gourmet funnel cake food truck in the world.Our motto is “Fun Food, Fun People, Fun Place!”.We not only serve traditional funnel cakes with powdered sugar, but also serve Funnels with Flair including gourmet funnel cakes, funnel fries, funnel swirls, bacon fries, Rocky Mountain FunNuts, and other delicious treats like The Fundae, A Fun Sundae! The Fun Crew serves up family fun and memorable experiences. The Funnels Food Truck attends local festivals, fairs, community events, weddings, corporate events, and private parties in the Denver Metro Area.
name: Funnels
